snippet.textDisplay:
YOU ARE ALL DUMBFUCK MORONS! !

YOU IDIOTS, IF YOU WANT TO WATCH THE ORIGINALS, WHY DO YOU TUNE INTO COKE STUDIO?

You guys need an education on music. Coke Studio tries to rework every original song and give it a transcendental sufiana feel. The original song was more like a quwali while Leslie has made a terrific attempt at giving it a sufi feel by reducing its tempo. Of all the songs in this debut season, this one is Lewis's best and it is ironic that he is facing maximum flak for  it.
